<MELItem itemNbr="31-61-11" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-31-61-11.1.2-31-61-11">
<Title>Electronic Checklist (ECL) System</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Electronic checklist is deactivated.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Established suitable checklist procedures are used.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>No maintenance action is required if the CHECKLIST DISABLED or CHECKLIST NOT AVAILABLE message is displayed on an MFD.</Para>
</Note>
<Para>Deactivate the electronic checklist (AMM DDG 31-61-11).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>On the Miscellaneous Systems Control (MISC SYSTEM CTRLS) page, set the ELECTRONIC CHECKLIST box to DISABLE.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Use established paper checklists.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>The rectangular icon symbol that precedes some alert messages will not be displayed.</Para>
</Note>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="31-61-11-01">
<Title>ECL Closed Loop Switch Indications</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="-" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided ECL line item override procedures are used when required to complete checklists.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Use the line item override (ITEM OVRD) key as required.</Para>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELSubItem>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>